OL,3,CResearch may shed light on difficulty
OL,4,Cin identifying The Traitors
OL,6,FNew research may explain why people's
OL,7,Fjudgments of the trustworthiness of
OL,8,Fgroups are often flawed, as seen in
OL,9,Fthe hit TV series The Traitors.
OL,11,FThe popular BBC show follows a group
OL,12,Fof contestants in which some become
OL,13,FTraitors and the remaining Faithful
OL,14,Fmust work together to eliminate them
OL,15,Ffrom the game and collect the prize
OL,16,Fmoney.
