OL,3,CResearch may shed light on difficulty
OL,4,Cin identifying The Traitors
OL,6,FIn the second series, screening now,
OL,7,Fthe Traitors have so far proved
OL,8,Felusive with the Faithful struggling
OL,9,Fto identify who should and should not
OL,10,Fbe trusted.
OL,12,FA study from the School of Psychology
OL,13,Fat the University of Aberdeen found
OL,14,Fwhen people encounter groups, they
OL,15,Fjudge their trustworthiness by
OL,16,Fcombining their facial features into
OL,17,Fone "composite face", which
OL,18,Fresearchers say can have serious
OL,19,Fimplications for how they perceive
OL,20,Fthem.
