OL,3,CResearch may shed light on difficulty
OL,4,Cin identifying The Traitors
OL,6,F"It is important to note, however,
OL,7,Fthat these judgments are neither
OL,8,Faccurate nor reliable.
OL,10,F"The link between facial features and
OL,11,Factual trustworthiness is far from
OL,12,Fperfect, and trustworthiness
OL,13,Fimpressions are insufficiently
OL,14,Faccurate to serve as reliable
OL,15,Ffoundations for real-world decision-
OL,16,Fmaking.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
