OL,6,FThis process is termed "ensemble
OL,7,Fperception" and is thought to be
OL,8,Fparticularly useful as it allows
OL,9,Fpeople to quickly extract perceived
OL,10,Fsocial information.
OL,12,FThe research, which was conducted
OL,13,Funder the supervision of lecturers Dr
OL,14,FMauro Manassi and Dr Clare Sutherland,
OL,15,Ffound this judgment is made in around
OL,16,Fa quarter of a second.
