OL,3,CResearch may shed light on difficulty
OL,4,Cin identifying The Traitors
OL,6,FMs Marini continued: "Traditionally,
OL,7,Fresearch has focused on
OL,8,Ftrustworthiness impressions at the
OL,9,Findividual face level by exploring how
OL,10,Fwe form trust judgments of single
OL,11,Findividuals.
OL,13,F"Obviously in everyday life, we often
OL,14,Fencounter groups of people rather than
OL,15,Fonly isolated individuals, so it is
OL,16,Fessential to understand how we form
OL,17,Fimpressions of groups.
OL,26,@nD@VOUuD@AOU
