OL,3,CResearch may shed light on difficulty
OL,4,Cin identifying The Traitors
OL,6,F"Fundamentally what is important is
OL,7,Fthat trustworthiness impressions of a
OL,8,Fgroup can potentially influence our
OL,9,Fbehaviour towards that group.
OL,11,F"But it is important to remember that
OL,12,Fwe are only talking about facial
OL,13,Ffeatures.
OL,15,F"Maybe what it really shows is that we
OL,16,Fshould focus on what people do, as
OL,17,Fopposed to judgments about whether we
OL,18,Flike the look of them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
