OL,3,CResearch may shed light on difficulty
OL,4,Cin identifying The Traitors
OL,6,F"This can explain why people may say
OL,7,Fthings like 'there's just something
OL,8,Fabout them I don't trust' or 'I don't
OL,9,Ftrust any of them', and yes, it may
OL,10,Fexplain why the Traitors are proving
OL,11,Fso elusive."
OL,13,FThe study is published in the journal
OL,14,FCognition.
OL,16,FThe latest series of The Traitors,
OL,17,Fhosted by Claudia Winkleman, concludes
OL,18,Fon BBC One on Friday.
